{"tid":459521,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我只係想有覺好訓","createTime":"2017-11-05T22:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T08:30:08.000Z","uid":41693,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b54dc1edf8e943513aaf68bd4463518efc87edb9","tid":459521,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:14:51.000Z","msg":"屋企細 同房有個關係好差既所謂阿哥<br />\n鼻鼾聲嘈到好似鑽地咁<br />\n咁多年黎 我要好似忍辱偷生咁等無咁響時<br />\n逼自己盡快訓 有時甚至訓著都嘈醒<br />\n早幾年讀書有Hall住係我人生除左bb之外<br />\n我諗係我訓得最好既時期 <br />\n但係今年讀完書Quit hall搬左翻屋企<br />\n出來做野要返Shift <br />\n朝早5點翻到屋企沖完涼只係想訓<br />\n但屋企一位 所謂既屋企人 鼻鼾聲嘈到好似鑽地咁<br />\n耳塞都無用<br />\n就算同佢嘈完 佢都唔會理我 嘈醒佢又會發癲搞到兩老唔開心 <br />\n我一直都好想搬出去住<br />\n但搵過好多 一係就劏房 唔見得會靜過依家<br />\n一係就好貴 我份糧比完家用扣完洗費 再比呢份租<br />\n應該真係無乜錢剩 <br />\n我認我垃圾搵唔到多錢 但我只係想有覺好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380b9bb431d929d5f0c96d51cde9bdbb7c4986c7","tid":459521,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:16:55.000Z","msg":"然後依家出去食個早餐 <br />\n應該要等佢起身我先有得訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5013c064f26dba9af161f7d2b2edcca16b99309","tid":459521,"uid":132088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:17:26.000Z","msg":"你出少少錢醫好佢啲鼻鼾囉"},{"pid":"b80e866f037e051f0a16fe6278e3e1322cf410e9","tid":459521,"uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:17:29.000Z","msg":"有冇試過食安眠藥<br />\n<br />\n快啲結婚搬出去住"},{"pid":"a62f5e8bf2365285828887446954513abcaf9f9e","tid":459521,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:20:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你出少少錢醫好佢啲鼻鼾囉</blockquote><br />\n同佢關係好差 大家無視對方"},{"pid":"cf9c64ddf99a5343eb280885684ae549bb1a8137","tid":459521,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過食安眠藥<br />\n<br />\n快啲結婚搬出去住</blockquote><br />\n佢唔會理我聽我講<br />\n<br />\n窮撚 就無謂害左個女仔 自己都養唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8901aaec64b234f3777206a8da73b459aa447e6","tid":459521,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:21:54.000Z","msg":"同你情況差唔多但你再差啲<br />\n好明你感受<br />\n出去搵人夾租啦"},{"pid":"9045ede44317709a5598ed1bc78891ef36cac473","tid":459521,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T22:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你情況差唔多但你再差啲<br />\n好明你感受<br />\n出去搵人夾租啦</blockquote><br />\n有無渠道可以搵到人夾租？ <br />\n我見好多都只係搵女仔夾"},{"pid":"0f445ea1c34cf90f5fd546637809d41a0bed6c09","tid":459521,"uid":155997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:13:36.000Z","msg":"其實鼻鼾大，好多時跟埋睡眠窒息。帶呼吸機瞓覺會冇鼻鼾聲"},{"pid":"a3d1ca474ebd8d59995d0ecaaad3d323d8cb4e8c","tid":459521,"uid":79839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:22:36.000Z","msg":"有無朋友出黎同你夾租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係夾租會貴過自己租劏房"},{"pid":"bcc978217f36b2e0fd5c93b77ba8f8ddcc6369a5","tid":459521,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實鼻鼾大，好多時跟埋睡眠窒息。帶呼吸機瞓覺會冇鼻鼾聲</blockquote><br />\n佢唔會為左我而特登帶個呼吸機訓"},{"pid":"cfe149ab59cb71fb82b169027c7d2a7bd9ae6a00","tid":459521,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T04:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無朋友出黎同你夾租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係夾租會貴過自己租劏房</blockquote><br />\n無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我都想搵人夾租 但係無朋友想出黎租"},{"pid":"7079c80489331eab8ba7fba9ac6737ac7f6dde23","tid":459521,"uid":89917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"訓客廳囉"},{"pid":"3ff420c9b29e4aab7fa75ee1ae9d208cbd853f53","tid":459521,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓客廳囉</blockquote><br />\n屋企細 嘈到廳都聽得好清楚"},{"pid":"39ff8fa8c0d837a4bd47509f61b6774d07f534b2","tid":459521,"uid":52146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"打鼻鼾真係好撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c05a58711f200de0cc84b49d1d6b435c2c9536","tid":459521,"uid":89917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>訓客廳囉</blockquote><br />\n屋企細 嘈到廳都聽得好清楚</blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過食安眠藥？我指你食"},{"pid":"e1f1da1dc5a64139b5e2f5d269d72abfdb124965","tid":459521,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>訓客廳囉</blockquote><br />\n屋企細 嘈到廳都聽得好清楚</blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過食安眠藥？我指你食</blockquote><br />\n無食過<br />\n但就算好攰好眼訓都因為太嘈訓唔到<br />\n佢訓上格床"}]}